Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.13,Sayo Asa - jap,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ　マキアもおいで
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.52,Sayo Asa - jap,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛んでおいでー！
